{"tid":2225390,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警喺荃灣拘捕一名司機 搜出「光復香港 時代革命」等標語單張","createTime":"2020-10-01T09:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:23:24.000Z","uid":44209,"like":18,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"55b8d569e9afb5b7d3cfd1d86fb20f9b0dc14fc5","tid":2225390,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YSLfg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YSLfg1.jpg&h=4a5c0598&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9akOB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9akOB2.jpg&h=466c3640&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dECOXvn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdECOXvn.jpg&h=8e3bd011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#荃灣<br />\n//警方今日（1日）於本港各區拘捕多名人士，其中在今午3時許，於屯門公路近荃灣翠豐臺一帶設路障截查車輛期間，發現一輛私家車的行車證過期，並在車上搜獲伸縮棍、頭盔、面具及大量宣傳單張，部分單張寫有涉嫌鼓吹香港獨立的標語。警方拘捕車上一名35歲男司機，涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途、駕駛無牌車輛，以及在沒有第三者保險而使用車輛等罪行被捕。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/klsinglennonwall/32909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fklsinglennonwall%2F32909&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=7d1e2eca\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/klsinglennonwall/32909</a>"},{"pid":"04dc0ed1584212ec651bd7c07b8841fe2d8c6641","tid":2225390,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c26f2e6d6cd80d12060efa0461fbd80c0d0f3a","tid":2225390,"uid":275370,"like":111,"dislike":10,"score":101,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"6145ba8d2e59396bc592ecc15efa9a7954419d7d","tid":2225390,"uid":273703,"