ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"今日為中秋正日，多名市民偕家人落街食飯慶祝，晚上近7時，荃灣路德圍多間餐廳門外均有人排隊等候，其間多架警車駛抵現場，之後近半百名身穿全套裝備的防暴警及便衣警員巡邏上址，又向途經的市民作出截查，但現場一直未有人聚集叫口號，甚至舉旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n其間防暴警要求在場的記者出示記者證，事件擾攘大約15分鐘，一名懷疑不足16歲的記者被警方帶上警車離開。另外，現場亦有兩名男子雙手被綁上索帶，被防暴警帶上警車，未知原因。"},{"pid":"c4897ab2a3f3f072344dea99ca2d07d2e10b8deb","tid":2225390,"uid":264387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13767976d7affd487bccdd294ddd046a52630e8d","tid":2225390,"uid":34410,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:52:03.000Z","msg":"旗悍都係伸縮棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鴨記大把唔去捉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"碌棍個握把五顏六色，擺到明老師督黑板大力小小都斷果啲啦，曱甴屈你駛講道理"},{"pid":"4242ed84cd208324478de4795d324e683cb8eda8","tid":2225390,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"281deba39bf220b7bb63ad77b7ab70d4ec318b31","tid":2225390,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"1928 #荃灣  #路德圍 #被捕人士<br />\n兩男被押上UK4137。<br />\n#立場<br />\n<br />\nSource: 實時"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"記者話係袋到搵到防毒面具+面巾"},{"pid":"89fc616bfc82fbf9b6b0fca6af6d1350c496ca2d","tid":2225390,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1cbddff7cfa386435db27cecd7d85e1db1f0337","tid":2225390,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f275994a8e924d32bb3e32e74c8312d4fffb3a","tid":2225390,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966fa2420e2fa896d2546053d546c6548809de5f","tid":2225390,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-